episodes.title: Reviewing THE PSYCHOLOGY OFSECRETS (MY ADVENTURES WITH MURDERERS, CULTS AND INFLUENCERS
episodes.description: Noted author ANDREW GOLD offers a most fascinating look at secrets, lies, manipulation and more. He studies this phenomenon, and how many of us use lies and manipulation to get our way. Cults, the myth of Santa, parents lying to children, and much more, make this a book that will keep you riveted to every word.
